== The Personal Publishing Manifest

Psychedelic Minimal CMS fÃ¼r Alles

See: http://github.com/maetl/tppm

== Install

Ruby and Rubygems, and the following gem dependencies are required:

 $> sudo gem install sinatra
 $> sudo gem install jsmin
 $> sudo gem install cssmin
 $> sudo gem install faker

To run the preview app:

 $> ruby preview.rb

Then go to: http://localhost:4567/preview/elements